        "time": 0.5,
        "side": 1
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "actor": 407010,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": -1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "我们单是要让自己的舰装听话就要费不少力。与其他阵营共存的话更需多加留心。要多谢46你的协助。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 0,
      "say": "没关系。齐柏林是我重要的朋友，出手帮你乃是理所当然。",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "actor": 407010,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": -1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "朋友…吗…呵呵，从没想过会被驱逐舰当做朋友，但是Z46的话…很不可思议的觉得没什么违和感呢",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 0,
      "say": "另外，我并没有做任何值得感谢的事。同为铁血舰，相互照应是理所当然",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "actor": 407010,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": -1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "既然如此，我也给你一个建议吧。46，你这个说话口气能否改一改？",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 0,
      "say": "齐柏林也没资格说我吧。不过，为何要改口气？",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "actor": 407010,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": -1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "你不是因为难以融入驱逐舰的氛围而烦恼着吗。那么不妨试着学一学？",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "actor": 407010,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": -1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "……和她们一样的说话方式。",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "actor": 401460,
      "side": 0,
      "say": "…………",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
